{"id":624752419,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"1 year, 11 months","timestamp":1642787071,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"14 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/624752419/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"8.4 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string s) {\n        vector<int>dict(256,-1);\n        int maxlen=0,window_start=-1;\n        for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++)\n        {\n            if(dict[s[i]]>window_start)\n                window_start=dict[s[i]];\n            dict[s[i]]=i;\n            maxlen=max(maxlen,i-window_start);\n        }\n        return maxlen;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
